{"prompt": "Develop a professional portfolio for a videographer. The primary color should be a striking amethyst purple.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Alex Chen - Videographer</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #663399; /* Amethyst Purple */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #663399 3px solid;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        #hero {\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x700/663399/FFFFFF?text=Professional+Videography') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 600px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(102, 51, 153, 0.5); /* Amethyst Purple overlay */\n        }\n        #hero .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            font-weight: lighter;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        section h2 {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: #663399; /* Amethyst Purple */\n        }\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .gallery-item {\n            background: #fff;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .gallery-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n        .gallery-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 3px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .gallery-item h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            color: #663399; /* Amethyst Purple */\n        }\n        #contact {\n            background-color: #663399; /* Amethyst Purple */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n        #contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        #contact label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Ensures padding doesn't affect width */\n        }\n        #contact textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n        }\n        #contact button {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            color: #663399; /* Amethyst Purple */\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: #f0f0f0;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        a {\n            color: #663399; /* Amethyst Purple */\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Alex Chen</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Capturing Stories Through Motion</h2>\n            <p>Creative Videography for Your Vision</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <p>\n                I'm Alex Chen, a passionate videographer dedicated to crafting compelling visual narratives. With a keen eye for detail and a love for storytelling, I bring projects to life through dynamic and engaging video content. Whether it's for brands, events, or personal projects, I strive to create videos that resonate and leave a lasting impression.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"portfolio\">\n            <h2>My Work</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/663399/FFFFFF?text=Project+1\" alt=\"Project 1 Thumbnail\">\n                    <h3>Brand Showcase Reel</h3>\n                    <p>A vibrant reel highlighting key aspects of a local business.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/663399/FFFFFF?text=Project+2\" alt=\"Project 2 Thumbnail\">\n                    <h3>Event Highlights</h3>\n                    <p>Dynamic coverage of a music festival's energetic atmosphere.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/663399/FFFFFF?text=Project+3\" alt=\"Project 3 Thumbnail\">\n                    <h3>Short Documentary</h3>\n                    <p>An intimate look into the life of a local artisan.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/663399/FFFFFF?text=Project+4\" alt=\"Project 4 Thumbnail\">\n                    <h3>Travel Vlog Series</h3>\n                    <p>Visually stunning episodes from various travel destinations.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Services</h2>\n            <p>\n                <ul>\n                    <li>Brand Storytelling</li>\n                    <li>Event Coverage</li>\n                    <li>Promotional Videos</li>\n                    <li>Documentaries</li>\n                    <li>Music Videos</li>\n                    <li>Short Films</li>\n                </ul>\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Alex Chen. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>\n                <a href=\"#\">LinkedIn</a> |\n                <a href=\"#\">Vimeo</a> |\n                <a href=\"#\">Instagram</a>\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Message sent! Thank you for reaching out.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}